'''贝一明'''（{{lang-en|'''Emanuel Pastreich'''}}，{{lang-ko|'''李萬烈'''}}，{{lang-ja|'''エマニユエル・パストリッチ'''}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://circlesandsquares.asia/bio/ |title=网站 Circles and Squares (2013-3-31). |access-date=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2013-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521020059/http://circlesandsquares.asia/bio/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；{{bd|1964年|10月16日}}，生于[[美国|美国]][[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]），活跃在[[韩国|韩国]]的美国学者。在东亚古典文学<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.princeton.edu/eap/events_archive/viewevent.xml?id=150 |title=The Reception of Chinese Vernacular Narrative in Korea and Japan, Emanuel Pastreich, Kyung Hee University |publisher=Princeton University East Asian Studies Program |date=October 1, 2012 |accessdate=November 30, 2012 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004232304/http://www.princeton.edu/eap/events_archive/viewevent.xml?id=150 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://eastasianstudies.research.yale.edu/events.php?timestamp=2012-10-3 |title=East Asia Colloquium Series: The Observable Mundane: The Reception of Chinese Vernacular Narrative in Korea and Japan |publisher=Yale University, The Council on East Asian Studies |date=October 3, 2012 |accessdate=November 30, 2012 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029190256/http://eastasianstudies.research.yale.edu/events.php?timestamp=2012-10-3 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Woo-young |last=Lee |url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20110626000290 |title=U.S. scholar explores Asian literature |publisher=Korea Herald |date=July 26, 2011 |accessdate=November 1, 2012 |archive-date=2018-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627062548/http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20110626000290 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Emanuel Pastreich |year=1999 |title=An alien vernacular: Okajima Kanzan’s popularization of the Chinese vernacular novel in eighteenth-century Japan |journal=SJS |volume=11 |issue=2 |pages=39–49 |publisher= |doi= |pmid= |pmc= |url=http://www.chinajapan.org/articles/11.2/11.2pastreich39-49.pdf |accessdate=November 3, 2012 |archive-date=2017-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171013120218/http://www.chinajapan.org/articles/11.2/11.2pastreich39-49.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，当代国际关系与技术等方面多有著文。帕斯特里希（Pastreich）于2020年2月宣布他竞选美国总统独立，并继续他的竞选活动，并发表了许多演讲，呼吁对安全和经济采取变革性的态度。<ref name="asiatimesonline">{{cite web |url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Korea/NL01Dg01.html |title=A new kind of scholar breaks ground in Korea |last=Arvind |first=Subadra |date=1 December 2012 |publisher=Asia Times Online |accessdate=2 December 2012 |archive-date=2016-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325132727/http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Korea/NL01Dg01.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.futureconference.or.kr/bs/content.php?co_id=KeynoteSpeech |title=Research, Innovation, Start-up and Employment (RISE) Keynote Speakers |publisher=Korean Ministry of Science, ICT, and Future Planning |date=21–22 May 2013 |accessdate=7 May 2013 |archive-date=2013-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130902014426/http://www.futureconference.or.kr/bs/content.php?co_id=KeynoteSpeech |dead-url=no }}</ref>

贝一明，现担任坐落于韩国首尔的[[亚洲研究所|亚洲研究所]]（The Asia Institute）理事长一职，同时在社会中还兼任[http://emi.earth/?l=zh-CN 地球治理研究院] {{Wayback|url=http://emi.earth/?l=zh-CN |date=20180706162006 }}院长以及国际大脑教育综合大学院的副校长。亚洲研究所以及地球治理研究院分别由贝一明本人于2007年和2018年设立。

==个人简介==
贝一明于1983年毕业于旧金山洛威尔高中，后就读于[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]]，于1987年毕业并获得学士学位，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pastreich.files.wordpress.com/2012/11/yale-diploma.jpg |title=耶鲁大学 Circles and Squares (2013-3-31). |access-date=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309234323/https://pastreich.files.wordpress.com/2012/11/yale-diploma.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref>大学期间曾赴台湾国立大学交流学习。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pastreich.files.wordpress.com/2012/11/taida-id.jpg |title=國立臺灣大學 Circles and Squares (2013-3-31). |access-date=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309215600/https://pastreich.files.wordpress.com/2012/11/taida-id.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref> 1991年贝一明用日文撰写并完成其硕士论文《论江户时代晚期的文人画家田能村竹田：诗与画的"无用"》，获得日本[[东京大学|东京大学]]比较文学硕士学位。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pastreich.files.wordpress.com/2012/11/tokyo-diploma.jpg |title=东京大学 Circles and Squares (2013-3-31). |access-date=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305210255/https://pastreich.files.wordpress.com/2012/11/tokyo-diploma.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref> 此后，贝一明回到美国，并于1998年获得[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]东亚问题研究博士学位。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Shin |first1=Gi-wook |last2=Robinson |first2=Michael |year=2001 |title=Colonial Modernity in Korea |url=http://books.google.co.kr/books?id=JMVgNnkZXAQC&pg=PA441&lpg=PA441&dq=%22emanuel+pastreich%22+Harvard&source=bl&ots=7gyCZ0pWK1&sig=FseWYkTmkpE_8ZYHdlKh7Ow9PLo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=26OcUPq2MayaiQfD44GYAg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=November 9, 2012 |page=441 |quote=See Emanuel Pastreich, "The Reception of Chinese Vernacular Narrative in Korea and Japan" (PhD diss., Harvard University, 1997), pp. 49-52 |ISBN=0674005945 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216223103/https://books.google.co.kr/books?id=JMVgNnkZXAQC&pg=PA441&lpg=PA441&dq=%22emanuel+pastreich%22+Harvard&source=bl&ots=7gyCZ0pWK1&sig=FseWYkTmkpE_8ZYHdlKh7Ow9PLo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=26OcUPq2MayaiQfD44GYAg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref> 毕业后，陆续在伊利诺伊大学香槟分校，<ref name="dailyillini">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailyillini.com/news/article_78f008f8-cebe-5d98-b018-61f826d74ab2.html |title=Debate about North Korea reaches students, faculty |last=Mellen |first=Brian |date=17 July 2006 |publisher=Daily Illini |accessdate=13 November 2012}}</ref><REF name>
{{cite web |url=http://acdis.illinois.edu/aboutacdis/profile.html&pid=115 |title=Contact Information: Emanuel Pastreich |publisher=ACDIS, University of Illinois |accessdate=13 November 2012 |archive-date=2012-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311073134/http://acdis.illinois.edu/aboutacdis/profile.html%26pid%3D115 |dead-url=no }}
</ref>乔治华盛顿大学<ref name="dailyillini" />及又松大学<ref name="Yalejournal">{{cite journal |last=Simon |first=Ian D. |year=2011 |title=Plans of Mice and Men: From Bench Science to Science Policy |journal=Yale J. Biol. Med. |volume=84 |issue=3 |pages=237–242 |publisher=Yale University |url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3178853/ |accessdate=14 November 2012 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216220602/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3178853/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>任副教授。贝一明之后还于2011年至2017年之间韩国[[慶熙大學|慶熙大學]]国际问题研究学院，任副教授一职。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hc.khu.ac.kr/english/04_faculty.php |title=Kyung Hee University's homepage (24 October 2012). |access-date=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624172422/http://hc.khu.ac.kr/english/04_faculty.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Hangukilbo">{{cite web |url=http://news.hankooki.com/lpage/culture/201211/h2012110721271484210.htm |script-title=ko:한국 어디로 가야하나… 석학들의 혜안 빌려 조망해봤죠: 경희대 페스트라이쉬 교수 '세계의 석학들, 한국의 미래를 말하다' 출간 |last=Cho |first=Eun-mi |date=7 November 2012 |publisher=Hanguk Ilbo |accessdate=9 November 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108233040/http://news.hankooki.com/lpage/culture/201211/h2012110721271484210.htm |archivedate=2012年11月8日 }}</ref>  2014年贝一明出版了最新著作《[[跨海求真|跨海求真: 哈佛博士论中美未来]]》.<ref name="chinesebook">{{cite book |last1=Pastreich |first1=Emanuel |year=2014年 |title=跨海求真: 哈佛博士论中美未来,亚洲研究所出版社 |accessdate=September 9, 2014 |ISBN=978-0-692-20612-6}}</ref>

