==工作==
贝一明目前为[[亚洲研究所|亚洲研究所]]理事长。亚洲研究所是一所[[智库|智库]]，致力引导[[东亚地区|东亚地区]]跨领域的研究合作，包括国际关系，环境<ref>{{cite web |first=Emanuel |last=Pastreich |url=http://truth-out.org/opinion/item/14901-leading-climate-fight-defense-could-preserve-and-protect-rather-than-kill-and-destroy |title=On Climate, Defense Could Preserve and Protect, Rather Than Kill and Destroy |publisher=Truthout |date=7 March 2013 |accessdate=8 March 2013 |archive-date=2017-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621040508/http://www.truth-out.org/opinion/item/14901-leading-climate-fight-defense-could-preserve-and-protect-rather-than-kill-and-destroy |dead-url=no }}</ref>与能源。<ref name="asiatimesonline" />2005－2007年，贝一明曾担任韩美合作社（KORUS House）执行官，韩美合作社位于华盛顿特区，为韩国驻美国大使馆智库。期间，他还担任《动态韩国》总编一职，<ref>{{cite web |first=Matthew |last=Weigand |url=http://www.koreaittimes.com/story/12924/american-daejeon |title=An American in Daejeon: How a Literature Professor Ended Up Deep in Korean Policy and Business |publisher=Korea IT Times |date=February 7, 2011 |accessdate=October 21, 2012 |archive-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206074634/http://www.koreaittimes.com/story/12924/american-daejeon |dead-url=no }}</ref>《动态韩国》杂志为韩国外交部所属刊物，<ref>{{cite thesis |type=Ph.D. |first=Susan I. |last=Kim |title=Changes and Continuities in Second-generation Korean American Families |publisher=City University of New York |year=2007 |page=39 |url=http://books.google.co.kr/books?id=dAJlH4oIn8IC&pg=PA39&lpg=PA39&dq=%22emanuel+pastreich%22+editor-in-chief&source=bl&ots=3U1WB38uOy&sig=KuJmpKx3AYiN1hWMdiVwxR7mQXw&hl=en&sa=X&ei=30arUPHXJaf8iQLZ7YGIAQ&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22emanuel%20pastreich%22%20editor-in-chief&f=false |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005002027/http://books.google.co.kr/books?id=dAJlH4oIn8IC&pg=PA39&lpg=PA39&dq=%22emanuel+pastreich%22+editor-in-chief&source=bl&ots=3U1WB38uOy&sig=KuJmpKx3AYiN1hWMdiVwxR7mQXw&hl=en&sa=X&ei=30arUPHXJaf8iQLZ7YGIAQ&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22emanuel%20pastreich%22%20editor-in-chief&f=false |archivedate=2013-10-05 |access-date=2013-03-31 }}</ref> 致力于介绍及推广韩国文化和社会。2007－2008年，贝一明曾任忠南道主管官员的国际关系与外商投资顾问。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.koreasociety.org/policy/policy/from_hermit_kingdom_to_global_hub_seoul_reinvents_its_cultural_identity.html |title=From Hermit Kingdom to Global Hub: Seoul Reinvents its Cultural Identity |publisher=The Korea Society |date=March 29, 2006 |accessdate=November 20, 2012 |archive-date=2013-04-15 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130415054240/http://www.koreasociety.org/policy/from_hermit_kingdom_to_global_hub_seoul_reinvents_its_cultural_identity.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

贝一明所著书籍及作品有：《朴智元小说作品：被忽视世界的解析》，本书为这位韩国朝鲜时代重要作家的作品集；《可触的方言：中文方言及其在江户时代的日本流行文学作品中的兴起与采用》，本书探讨了中文方言在日本文学中的影响和作用；《生命在于方向而非速度：生活在韩国的鲁滨逊》，本书记录了贝一明本人在韩国的生活经历；此外，还有《全球学者谈韩国未来》，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2012112301032903001001 |script-title=ko:한국, 춘추전국 周 닮아… 주변국에 `영감' 주는 나라 될 것 |first=Jinsu |last=Ye |publisher=Munhwa Ilbo |date=November 23, 2012 |accessdate=November 28, 2012 |archive-date=2013-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131131802/http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2012112301032903001001 |dead-url=no }}</ref>贝一明就"当代韩国"这一课题采访了一些主要学者，包括[[弗朗西斯·福山|弗朗西斯·福山]]、[[拉芮·维克森|拉芮·维克森]]以及[[诺姆·乔姆斯基|诺姆·乔姆斯基]]等，本书即是收录了这一系列访谈记录。<ref name="asiatimesonline" />

